<div
  style="background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 60px 37px 30px 37px"
>

  <h2>Hi {{candidateName}},</h2>

  <h1
    style="color: #8B0000; margin-top: 10px; font-size: 32px"
  >{{verificationType}}
    Attestation Request</h1>
  <p>
    Nneoma Okoro is requesting to run
    {{attestationType}}
    Verification on the Job you filled on your resume.
  </p>

  <div
    style="background-color: #FFF0F0; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #B01116; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0;"
  >
    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; color: #53090B">
      <tr
        style="padding: 12px 0; font-weight: 500; border-bottom: 1px solid #46383D;"
      >
        <td style="padding: 12px 0; color: #321011C7; ">By</td>
        <td
          style="padding: 12px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: semi-bold; font-size: 20px"
        >{{companyName}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr
        style="padding: 12px 0; font-weight: 500; border-bottom: 1px solid #46383D;"
      >
        <td style="padding: 12px 0; color: #321011C7; ">For</td>
        <td
          style="padding: 12px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: semi-bold; font-size: 20px"
        >{{for}} Coco Melon LTD</td>
      </tr>
      <tr
        style="padding: 12px 0; font-weight: 500; border-bottom: 1px solid #46383D;"
      >
        <td style="padding: 12px 0; color: #321011C7;">Role</td>
        <td
          style="padding: 12px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: semi-bold; font-size: 20px"
        >{{jobRole}} </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 12px 0px 0px 0px; color: #321011C7;">Duration</td>
        <td
          style="padding: 12px 0 0px 0px; text-align: right;  font-weight: semi-bold; font-size: 20px"
        >{{duration}} 24 June 2021 - 23 Jan 2024</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div
    style="background-color: #FFD7D9; color: #3C0103; border-radius: 8px; padding: 30px 20px; margin: 30px 0; text-align: center; background-image: url('https://example.com/pattern.png'); background-size: cover; background-blend-mode: overlay;"
  >
    <h2 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #3C0103;">What to
      Expect</h2>

    <div style="margin: 8px 0;">Your have Complete KYC</div>
    <div>Attest to Job Histroy</div>
    <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content: center;">

      <a
        href="{{verificationUrl}}"
        style="display: block; background-color: #B11116; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 25px; text-align: center; width: 50%;"
      >
        Attest
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>This request will expire in
    {{expiryDays}}
    days. Please complete the verification before the expiration date. If the
    verification is not completed within this timeframe, you will no longer be
    able to proceed with it.</p>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 40px 0;">
    <div style="display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px; text-align: center;">
      <div
        style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 50%; width: 60px; height: 60px; line-height: 60px; margin: 0 auto;"
      >{{days}}</div>
      <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #777; margin-top: 5px;">DAY</div>
    </div>
    <div style="display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px; text-align: center;">
      <div
        style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 50%; width: 60px; height: 60px; line-height: 60px; margin: 0 auto;"
      >{{hours}}</div>
      <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #777; margin-top: 5px;">HOUR</div>
    </div>
    <div style="display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px; text-align: center;">
      <div
        style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 50%; width: 60px; height: 60px; line-height: 60px; margin: 0 auto;"
      >{{minutes}}</div>
      <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #777; margin-top: 5px;">MINUTES</div>
    </div>
    <div style="display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px; text-align: center;">
      <div
        style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 50%; width: 60px; height: 60px; line-height: 60px; margin: 0 auto;"
      >{{seconds}}</div>
      <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #777; margin-top: 5px;">SECONDS</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>Your can contact
    <span style="color: #191847; font-size: semi-bold;">{{contactPerson}}</span>
    for more clarification if need.</p>

  <table
    style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0;  color: #200506"
  >
    <tr>
      <td
        style="padding: 12px 0; color: #777; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"
      >Telephone</td>
      <td
        style="padding: 12px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 500; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 20px"
      >{{companyPhone}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td
        style="padding: 12px 0; color: #777; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"
      >Email Address</td>
      <td
        style="padding: 12px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 500; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 20px"
      >{{companyEmail}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td
        style="padding: 12px 0; color: #777; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"
      >Contact Address</td>
      <td
        style="padding: 12px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 500; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 20px"
      >{{companyAddress}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  <p>Your can contact the company seeking the Verification request below</p>

  <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td
        style="padding: 12px 0; color: #777; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"
      >Telephone</td>
      <td
        style="padding: 12px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 500; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 20px"
      >{{companyPhone}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td
        style="padding: 12px 0; color: #777; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"
      >Email Address</td>
      <td
        style="padding: 12px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 500; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 20px"
      >{{companyEmail}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td
        style="padding: 12px 0; color: #777; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"
      >Contact Address</td>
      <td
        style="padding: 12px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: 500; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;  font-size: 20px"
      >{{companyAddress}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
    <p style="font-weight: bold;">Do you not recognise this attestation request?</p>
    <p>Just reply to this email or click
      <a
        href="{{reportUrl}}"
        style="color: #E92027; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: bold"
      >Report</a>
      to report this attestation request</p>
  </div>

</div>